## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="47f77-102">默认情况下<xref:System.Object>作为类型自变量封送`VARIANT`类型，其中的对象类型决定`VARTYPE`的值`VARIANT`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47f77-102">By default, <xref:System.Object> type arguments are marshaled as a `VARIANT` type, where the object type determines the `VARTYPE` value of the `VARIANT`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="47f77-103"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>键入必须作为传递<xref:System.Object>要作为封送类型`VARIANT`类型的`VT_ERROR`; 否则为<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>类型被封送为整数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47f77-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type must to be passed as an <xref:System.Object> type to be marshaled as a `VARIANT` of type `VT_ERROR`, otherwise the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type is marshaled as an integer.</span></span>  
  
